### Get all blogs
GET http://localhost:3001/api/blogs

### Create a new blog
POST http://localhost:3001/api/blogs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My first blog",
  "author": "Jane Dev",
  "url": "https://example.com/my-first-blog",
  "likes": 3
}

### Create a blog without likes (defaults to 0)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/blogs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Zero like default",
  "author": "Anon",
  "url": "https://example.com/zero"
}

### Bad request (missing title/url)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/blogs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "author": "Nobody",
  "likes": 10
}